{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_107","type":"agent_message","text":"The key detail is that `AlgorithmParameters.getInstance(\"2.16.840.1.101.3.4.1.42\")` fails on plain SunJCE even on the JVM; the real driver succeeds because it first installs the BouncyCastle provider. I’m switching the local shim to match that behavior and then querying BC’s provider registry for the exact `AlgorithmParameters` implementation class behind that OID."}}
{"type":"item.started","item":{"id":"item_108","type":"command_execution","command":"/usr/bin/bash -lc \"cat <<'EOF' > /tmp/PrintBcAlgoParams.java\nimport java.security.*;\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider;\npublic class PrintBcAlgoParams {\n  public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n    String alg = \\\"2.16.840.1.101.3.4.1.42\\\";\n    Security.addProvider(new BouncyCastleProvider());\n    for (Provider p : Security.getProviders()) {\n      Provider.Service s = p.getService(\\\"AlgorithmParameters\\\", alg);\n      if (s \"'!= null) {\n        System.out.println(\"provider=\" + p.getName() + \" class=\" + s.getClassName());\n      }\n    }\n    AlgorithmParameters ap = AlgorithmParameters.getInstance(alg);\n    System.out.println(\"instance provider=\" + ap.getProvider().getName() + \" class=\" + ap.getClass().getName());\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\"$JAVA_HOME/bin/javac\" -cp ~/.m2/repository/org/bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15on/1.70/bcprov-jdk15on-1.70.jar /tmp/PrintBcAlgoParams.java\n\"$JAVA_HOME/bin/java\" -cp /tmp:~/.m2/repository/org/bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15on/1.70/bcprov-jdk15on-1.70.jar PrintBcAlgoParams'","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":null,"status":"in_progress"}}
{"type":"item.started","item":{"id":"item_109","type":"command_execution","command":"/usr/bin/bash -lc \"cat <<'EOF' > /tmp/PrintBcAliases.java\nimport java.security.*;\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.BouncyCastleProvider;\npublic class PrintBcAliases {\n  public static void main(String[] args) {\n    Security.addProvider(new BouncyCastleProvider());\n    Provider p = Security.getProvider(\\\"BC\\\");\n    p.entrySet().stream()\n      .filter(e -> e.getKey().toString().contains(\\\"2.16.840.1.101.3.4.1.42\\\") || e.getValue().toString().contains(\\\"AlgorithmParametersSpi\"'$AESCCM\"))\n      .forEach(System.out::println);\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\"$JAVA_HOME/bin/javac\" -cp ~/.m2/repository/org/bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15on/1.70/bcprov-jdk15on-1.70.jar /tmp/PrintBcAliases.java\n\"$JAVA_HOME/bin/java\" -cp /tmp:~/.m2/repository/org/bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15on/1.70/bcprov-jdk15on-1.70.jar PrintBcAliases'","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":null,"status":"in_progress"}}
